snippet.title: MLB 11 The Show (PS3) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A full game of MLB 11 The Show, a baseball video game by Sony and San Diego Studio. PlayStation 3 version. Houston Astros at Seattle Mariners.

You can check out the PS2 version of the game here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wjMlnFpik3w
